      "author_association" : "MEMBER",
      "body" : "The issue is that newer versions of bdb produce wallet files which are not backward compatible, thus will not load in official binaries using 4.8. If you don't care about this, you can configure using --with-incompatible-bdb to force it to use a newer version. Another alternative is --disable-wallet to avoid the bdb dependency altogether.\n",
      "created_at" : "2015-02-18T09:39:16Z",
      "html_url" : "https://github.com/bitcoin/bitcoin/issues/3686#issuecomment-74836708",
